@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    <strong>ForgeRealm</strong> is a demonstration project created for educational
    and recruitment purposes. This application does not collect, store, or process
    any real personal data.
</p>

<h3>Data Usage</h3>
<ul>
    <li>All player, building, and resource data is fictional.</li>
    <li>Information shown in the application is stored only in a local development database.</li>
    <li>No third-party services, cookies, or tracking tools are used.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Security</h3>
<p>
    The project follows standard <strong>ASP.NET Core MVC</strong> best practices
    for data validation, database access, and separation of concerns, ensuring a
    secure and well-structured backend architecture.
</p>

<h3>Project Purpose</h3>
<p>
    ForgeRealm simulates core systems found in strategy and city-building games,
    including player progression, building upgrades, and resource management.
</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> No personal data is collected.</p>

